Package: rDNA
Version: 2.0.4
Date: 2018-01-25
Title: R Bindings for the Discourse Network Analyzer
Authors@R: c( person("Philip", "Leifeld", email = "Philip.Leifeld@glasgow.ac.uk", role =
    c("aut", "cre", "cph")), 
    person("Johannes", "Gruber", email = "j.gruber.1@research.gla.ac.uk", role = "ctb"))
Maintainer: Philip Leifeld <philip.leifeld@glasgow.ac.uk>
Description: Control the Java software Discourse Network Analyzer (DNA) from
    within R. Network matrices and attributes of nodes can be transferred 
    directly into R.
